"       This single vimrc is organized so that each plugin section maps
"       to a future lazy.nvim plugin spec file. The planned migration:
"
"         - Each "Plugin Settings: <name>" section → lua/plugins/<name>.lua
"         - General Settings → lua/config/options.lua
"         - General Mappings → lua/config/keymaps.lua
"         - General Functions → lua/config/functions.lua
"         - Filetype Autocmds → lua/config/autocmds.lua
