"   Filetype Autocmds ............. non-plugin filetype detection & overrides
"   Plugin Settings (alphabetical)  per-plugin config (~30 sections)
"   General Mappings .............. non-plugin key bindings by category
"   General Functions ............. utility functions (Incr, SmoothScroll, etc.)
"
" Known issues:
